<A NAME="topicMenuAlignMeshes"></A>

<H2>Align meshes</H2>
This menu item is used to perform an ICP operation.<P>

<H2>Usage</H2>

<OL>

<LI>
Select tow meshs in the mesh tree (The first selected will be the source and the second the target).

<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><img align="center" src="multipleMeshTreeSelection.png"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>


<LI>
Start the tool using the Menu "Filters > Align meshes".

<LI>
Select the landmarks points in the source mesh. When you finish press the enter key.

<LI>
Select the same number of landmarks points in the target mesh. When you finish press the enter key.

<LI>
The source mesh will be updated.


</OL>

